“After searching high and low for Medicine Woman, I was at a local dispensary and tried out Nurse Jackie based on the tested %
Loved how the strain smoked enough to go back & get more, and when I did, I realized why I liked it so much, one of its parents: Medicine Woman! Great for cramps and other pains, every chance I find it, I get it!”
“This is a great sativa strain. I thoroughly enjoyed it. I had some good organic N Jackie. But I'd bet the hydro version is KILLA!!!”
“Got this from Attis Trading on SE Gladstone. This is literally my #1 favorite strain.”

“Quickly becoming a top five for me. I love the Medicine Woman. Don't believe I've  tried Jack the Ripper, but this cross (when grown properly and will lots of LOVE) has a beautifully complex flavor profile, with either a stronger lemonene zing or this heavy citrus taste through and through. The stone goes straight to the eye's, but clear; very clear. Clean. Focused. Obviously it's not with out it's 80% plus Sativa ge...”
“headache relief is the name of the game. in my only use (so far) of Nurse Jackie, the low grade headache was resolved”

“I have to say that I have become a patient... and will now forever be loyal!! I love the way it makes you feel tingly and mellow. Straight stress and stress headache KILLER! Very nice and tasty to boot!”
“Excellent medicine!!  I curse the company who no longer markets the cartridge in Oregon!  Apparently they weren't making enough money on the strain so to hell with the patients who depended on it.”
“This strain is tasty, smooth, and doesn't make me too busy". I can focus and be productive while (usually eliminating) dealing with migraine pain. If I know a migraine is coming
column4: I will head it off with a little Nurse Jackie. Nine times out of ten I will not need a rescue pharmaceutical (i.e. Zomig

“It makes Getting Doug With High the greatest thing ever!”
“This is an amazing anytime strain. Beautifully clear meddy stone. Great for my neuropathic pain. I really dig this medicine.”
“this is loud as fuck, one of the best I have had.”
“Strong sativa...very energetic, clear, eye buzzing euphoria.”

“Smells like lemon scented pine sol and tastes very lemony and piney with a hint of rubber and something else I can't quite put my finger on yet. The high is very sativa, hitting right in the third eye and top of the head. Very mentally uplifting, pulls my head up into the clouds.  Very smooth vape, with no coughing. I find this to be a very pleasant almost pure sativa. No headache, dizziness or paranoia. Quite relaxi...”
“A chill high relaxing”
“Jack The Ripper x Medicine Woman Cross, very beautifully done. Flower is potent and heady, with a great rosey taste couple with some Earthiness. Good Sativa, and Highly recommended”
“The only thing I didn't like about this strain was that it was harsh on my throat and lungs, using a volcano vaporizer. Pleasant taste and decent effects, but didn't last super long.”
“love”
“Loving this Sativa 🍁”

“omg great buds dont normally care for sativas i prefer indicas or indica dominant but this strain was amazing helped my spasms eased my insomnia withouth making me overly tired and took my back pain right away”
“Man I got this last night for my headache who needs tylenol when you have Nurse Jackie my wife loves it”
“Love Nurse Jackie! She really pushes the creativity.”
“delicious Day time Tree. very flavorful always a Delight!”

“A True, Real Deal, Genuine Sativa!  Feel: Some energy but Not too energetic and finely tuned focus!  Happy!  Greatest head high in a while! Very mellow and happy. In the Zone!  Taste: Green apple or sweet, earthy and piney.  Smell:  blue berry or grape and piney/skunky.  Looks like a true sativa as well, with  plump but not dence Nugs. Very piney look and nice greens with purple under tones”
“not awesome harsh on throught.”
“Sativa Sucks !!!”

“The sample I had was not cured at all. It was a bit too dry. I rehydrated it and cured it for a few days. Made for a smoother smoke but still not what I was hoping. It was a clearheaded high with a short duration. This was on my to grow list but now I am not sure. THC 23.8 CBD .05 CBN .1”
“Where the hell is Nurse Jackie!!!!!!”
